/* Padding
padding: 40px;-> adding the space to the border and the content.
Height and widht->
when use the percentage ->it will cover the amount of the screen with regards t0 screen size 
max-width -> Allows authors to constrain content width to a certain range.

min-width -> Allows authors to constrain content width to a certain range.
outline-style -> Allows authors to set the style of the outline.
outline-offset-> Allows authors to set the offset of the outline.
*/



